    'timeline.title': 'My Story',
    'timeline.subtitle': 'How letters became sound, and code became the way',
    'timeline.curiosity.title': 'Curiosity',
    'timeline.curiosity.desc': 'It all started with a simple question: "How does this work?". First experiments with code, the magic of turning symbols into living interfaces. It wasn\'t just a hobby, but the discovery of a new world where logic meets art.',
    'timeline.stack.title': 'C++ & ASM â†’ Python â†’ Rust',
    'timeline.stack.desc': 'A journey from low-level C++ and Assembly, where every byte counts, through the flexibility of Python to the reliability of Rust. I learned to value memory control and type safety, choosing the tool for the task, not the other way around.',
    'timeline.club.title': 'Olympiads and Club',
    'timeline.club.desc': 'Olympiads tempered my character, and leading the IT club taught me responsibility. Sharing knowledge turned out to be as exciting as gaining it. We are building a community where technology brings people together.',
    'timeline.achievements.title': 'Achievements',
    'timeline.achievements.desc': 'From simple scripts to complex GUI applications and Telegram bots with thousands of users. My projects don\'t just live in repositories; they bring real value. Every error is a lesson, every line of code is a step forward.',
    'timeline.tbank.title': 'T-Bank Education',
    'timeline.tbank.desc': 'Participating in the T-Bank "Algorithms and Data Structures" project was a turning point. Deep diving into theory, solving complex problems, and working with mentors allowed me to reach a new level of engineering thinking.',
    'timeline.growth.title': 'Active Growth',
    'timeline.growth.desc': 'The IT world never stands still, and neither do I. Actively learning modern Web, practicing technical translations, and broadening my horizons. My goal is to become a T-shaped specialist capable of solving any challenge.',
